'''溫斯坦影業''' (The Weinstein Company，'''TWC''') 是一家美国电影公司，由[[哈維·溫斯坦|哈維·溫斯坦]]和[[鲍勃·溫斯坦|鲍勃·溫斯坦]]兄弟在离开[[米拉麥克斯影業|米拉麥克斯影業]]后于2005年创建，2018年破产，被Lantern Capital收购之后成为[[灯笼娛樂|灯笼娛樂]]。

該公司於2017年10月解雇了聯合創始人兼首席執行官哈維·溫斯坦，此前有70多名女性出面指控他進行性騷擾，毆打或強姦。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Barnes|first1=Brooks|title=Harvey Weinstein, Fired on Oct. 8, Resigns from Company's Board|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/10/17/business/media/harvey-weinstein-sexual-harassment.html|accessdate=October 24, 2017|date=October 17, 2017|archive-date=2017-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171023220217/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/10/17/business/media/harvey-weinstein-sexual-harassment.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2018年2月26日，溫斯坦影業在一份聲明中宣布，在與總統[[奥巴马|奥巴马]]領導下的小企業管理局前負責人瑪麗亞康特雷拉斯·斯威特（Maria Contreras-Sweet）領導​​的一個投資集團的收購協議破產後，將宣布破產。<ref name="nyt20180226">{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2018/02/26/business/weinstein-bankruptcy-deal.html|title=Weinstein Co. Will File for Bankruptcy After Deal Talks Collapse|last=Barnes|first=Brooks|date=February 26, 2018|work=The New York Times|accessdate=February 26, 2018|archive-date=2018-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180226072112/https://www.nytimes.com/2018/02/26/business/weinstein-bankruptcy-deal.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="comingsoon926683">{{cite web|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/925683-the-weinstein-company-to-declare-bankruptcy-after-sale-talks-fail|title=The Weinstein Company to Declare Bankruptcy After Sale Talks Fail|website=ComingSoon.net|last1=Perry|first1=Spencer|date=February 26, 2018|accessdate=February 27, 2018|archive-date=2018-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180226170236/http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/925683-the-weinstein-company-to-declare-bankruptcy-after-sale-talks-fail|dead-url=no}}</ref> 然而，令人驚訝的是，TWC董事會和投資集團於2018年3月1日證實，他們達成了TWC將以5億美元出售其所有資產的交易。<ref name="latimes20180301">{{cite web|title=Former Obama administration official has reached a deal to buy Weinstein Co. assets|last=Faughnder|first=Ryan|url=http://www.latimes.com/business/hollywood/la-fi-ct-weinstein-company-sale-20180301-story.html|work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|date=March 1, 2018|accessdate=March 2, 2018|archive-date=2018-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180302140113/http://www.latimes.com/business/hollywood/la-fi-ct-weinstein-company-sale-20180301-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="deadline1202307564">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2018/03/weinstein-company-deal-board-of-directors-maria-contreras-sweet-harvey-weinstein-1202307564/|title=TWC Board, New York AG Confirm Maria Contreras-Sweet Group Has Acquired Weinstein Company Assets|last=Chmielewski|first=Dawn|website=Deadline Hollywood|date=March 2, 2018|accessdate=March 2, 2018|archive-date=2018-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180302163930/http://deadline.com/2018/03/weinstein-company-deal-board-of-directors-maria-contreras-sweet-harvey-weinstein-1202307564/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2018年3月6日，該工作室公佈了額外的5000萬美元債務後，收購交易再度崩潰。<ref>{{cite web|title=Planned Sale of the Weinstein Company Collapses Again|last=Barnes|first=Brooke|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2018/03/06/business/media/weinstein-company-sale.html|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|date=March 6, 2018|accessdate=March 21, 2018|archive-date=2018-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180321002021/https://www.nytimes.com/2018/03/06/business/media/weinstein-company-sale.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 該公司於2018年3月19日申請破產保護。<ref>{{cite web|title=Weinstein Company files for bankruptcy|work=BBC News|date=March 20, 2018|accessdate=March 20, 2018|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-43466469|archive-date=2021-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210307234517/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-43466469|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2018年5月1日，Lantern Capital成為該公司破產拍賣的贏家。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2018/05/weinstein-company-lantern-capital-winner-bankruptcy-auction-1202380875|title=Weinstein Company Declares Lantern Capital The Winner Of Bankruptcy Auction, Rival Bidder Responds|last=Chmielewski|first=Dawn|website=Deadline Hollywood|date=May 1, 2018|accessdate=May 6, 2018|archive-date=2018-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180503112338/http://deadline.com/2018/05/weinstein-company-lantern-capital-winner-bankruptcy-auction-1202380875/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2018年7月16日，宣布該公司將更名為灯笼娛樂。

